description: The RTSP URL cannot be played directly in browsers. Run the FFmpeg command below to convert RTSP to HLS, then use the hlsUrl in the app.
ffmpegCommand: ffmpeg -i "rtsp://rtspstream:L5Aoo_Bv1cDagNLehZkyy@zephyr.rtsp.stream/movie" -c:v libx264 -preset ultrafast -tune zerolatency -c:a aac -f hls -hls_time 2 -hls_list_size 3 -hls_flags delete_segments -start_number 1 stream.m3u8
